                            <comment id="15933106" author="jira-bot" created="Mon, 20 Mar 2017 17:20:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1787815 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/branches/2.0&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
